text: Uka jach'a alay qullu patan Mecca ukawjan samarañana, kuywax wali jayankapuniwa, ukhamarak janiw khitin uñjatakisa.
translated_text:
Central Aymara: Uka jach'a alay qullu patan Mecca ukawjan samarañana, kuywax wali jayankapuniwa, ukhamarak janiw khitin uñjatakisa. 
English:: The Central Aymara people of the region of Mecca, in the north of the country, have been preparing for a long time for the arrival of the pilgrims, and have built a special place for them to stay.
